### Login as a verified user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "your-verified-user@example.com",
  "password": "your-password"
}

### Set this manually after login in REST Client
@token = paste-token-here

### Inventory list
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search inventory
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory?search=coffee
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create inventory item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "TEA-500",
  "name": "Assam Breakfast Tea",
  "category": "Grocery",
  "supplier": "Valley Tea Co",
  "quantity": 30,
  "reorderPoint": 12,
  "unitCost": 3.25,
  "retailPrice": 8.99,
  "leadTimeDays": 5,
  "location": "Aisle 1",
  "notes": "Premium shelf",
  "lastRestockDate": "2026-05-27",
  "lastRestockQuantity": 30
}

### Adjust stock
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/1/stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantityChange": 12,
  "reason": "Supplier delivery received"
}

### Restock summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/restock/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create restock order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/restock/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 2,
  "requestedQuantity": 24
}

### Mark restock order received
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/restock/orders/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "RECEIVED"
}

### Managers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/managers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Activity logs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/activity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
